fields.reviewer_message:
You guys are doing really good. That is a really good intitiative. Health is something that everyone should be concerned about as from outside one may look fine but from inside things may not look that good, so we should pay attention to every single thing that is troubling us and this is where you guys are shining... with the help of AI it is now easy to track those diseases and provide a possible cure.
Great work.... good luck with this project...
Cheers
Interactive User Interface. I used this site to check my mental health condition and to determine my diet plan and the result was quite precise.
the ui experience is smooth and information provided by website on stuff is well explained and to the point. Interaction with the website is super easy and smooth.  Good work done by the creators.

Its convenient to use this app. Pt. can keep check over his/her health status & accordingly can contact to doctor timely . 
This is covering almost major health problems of major population of India .
It will be great help to doctors for giving diagnosis.
